parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature wear of rear brakes can lead to reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potentially cause accidents, especially if the driver is not aware of the issue.
symptoms: Grinding or scraping noise from the rear brakes
uneven wear on the rear brake pads
metal-to-metal contact
and in some cases
complete brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the rear brake line can cause sudden loss of braking power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden loss of brake pedal
brake pedal goes to the floor
and loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Issues with the electronic braking system can cause unpredictable braking behavior, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Unusual scraping sound
slight loss of braking power
and premature wear of rear brake pads.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch/actuator can cause the door to not lock, potentially leading to safety risks, such as theft or unauthorized access to the vehicle.
symptoms: Door will not lock with inside door lock
key fob
or upon auto-lock activation; abnormal sounds when auto-locking; door may not lock intermittently with auto-lock feature and/or key fob.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the start/stop system can cause the vehicle to not turn on, potentially leaving the driver stranded or in a hazardous situation.
symptoms: Vehicle will not turn on while using the start/stop feature; requires complete shutdown and restart to resolve.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the bearing in the left front wheel can cause vibrations, noise, and potentially lead to wheel failure, affecting vehicle safety and performance.
symptoms: Abnormal noise or vibrations from the left front wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions, inconvenience, and potentially affect vehicle safety features, such as the rearview camera.
symptoms: Radio shuts down unexpectedly
even when reverse camera is active.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of advanced safety features, such as front collision warning and auto braking, can increase the risk of accidents and compromise vehicle safety.
symptoms: False activation of front collision warning and auto braking on clear roads with no obstruction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electric parking brake can cause unexpected engagement, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Electric parking brake engages unexpectedly
even when the vehicle is in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the lane departure system can cause the vehicle to drift out of its lane, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle tends to depart from its lane
even when driving straight or around corners.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, potentially leading to airbag malfunction or failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
airbag malfunction or failure to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed Recall Repair for Airbag Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repair for the airbag recall can increase the risk of injury or death due to airbag malfunction or failure to deploy in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
notification of recall but parts are not available.
